Story_Texts.SourceString: You've entered the domain of the evil sea god, Aipaloovik.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: You've entered the domain of the evil sea god, Aipaloovik.

Story_Texts.SourceString: He brought death to the Great River, freezing it down to the soil below the riverbed.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: He brought death to the Great River, freezing it down to the soil below the riverbed.

Story_Texts.SourceString: You cannot restore the river, but you can exact revenge!
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: You cannot restore the river, but you can exact revenge!

Story_Texts.SourceString: Defeat him, then bind him to your will!
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Defeat him, then bind him to your will!
